  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5798405/" class="title-link">大唐明月 月华如练</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5798405"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/55826588/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u55826588-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55826588/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">韵韵轩</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-03-03"
      class="main-meta">2013-03-03 14:54:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5798405_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        蓝云舒的《大唐明月》悄然无息地呈现，相见恨晚，爱不释手。感谢书友繁花的极力推荐，让我没有错过。作为资深的类型小说读者，我以为《大唐明月》在历史与言情小说类型中更偏向前者。小说男主人公裴行俭是唐高宗时赫赫有名的儒将，《大唐明月》以他一生的传奇为主线，言...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5798405/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">15有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5798405_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5798405_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





